    <summary>Create color swatches for configurable products. Includes image zoom.</summary>
    <description>The Configurable Colors extensions allows users to create color swatches for products. Swatches can be made using HTML color names, Hex Values, Classes, or images.&#xD;
&#xD;
The Configurable Colors extension also controls the display of the thumb and large images. The sizes for these images can be set in the Admin interface. &#xD;
&#xD;
The Configurable Colors extension also comes with an image zoom component. The size of the zoom image is also configurable.  </description>
